  "title": "Site Engineer - Mechanical / Piping (Process Plant)",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li><li><strong>Basic $ 3000 to $ 5000 + Variable Bonus + AWS</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: West (Pioneer) – working on-site</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><br /></p><ul><li><strong>Liaise with clients on-site for project/job requirements and walkdowns</strong></li><li>Propose mechanical/piping/engineering solutions based on site needs</li><li><strong>Prepare cost estimates, material take-offs, and project quotations</strong></li><li>Source materials, equipment, and subcontractor quotations</li><li><strong>Plan and coordinate manpower and job execution (site, fabrication shop, etc.)</strong></li><li>Review and interpret drawings (isometric, piping plans, structural)</li><li><strong>Edit and update CAD drawings, as-built records, and field design changes</strong></li><li>Ensure work complies with codes, specifications, and client requirements</li><li><strong>Manage RFIs and project documentation</strong></li><li>Assist in safety documentation (e.g., MSRA, lifting plans, fall prevention plans)</li><li><strong>Coordinate with internal teams and subcontractors to ensure project success</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p><br /></p><ul><li><strong>Diploma or Degree in Mechanical Engineering or related field</strong></li><li><strong>2–5 years’ experience in process plant / construction / maintenance projects</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>NG DIAUM YEE (R2198031)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
